---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
import CyberBackground from '../components/CyberBackground.astro';
import IdentityReveal from '../components/IdentityReveal.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="Profile: Evan"
	description="Profile and technical capabilities of Evan"
>
	<!-- Custom Title with Smooth Flow Animation -->
	<span slot="title" class="animated-title">Evan</span>

	<div class="profile-container">
		
		<!-- Section 1: Introduction -->
		<section class="intro">
			<p class="terminal-text">
				<span class="prompt">root@Evan:~$</span> cat mission_statement.txt<br>
				<span class="output">
					Code is not law. It is a puzzle waiting to be solved.<br>
					We specialize in dissecting the unseen layers of software protection. From <span class="highlight">Kernel-level</span> analysis to <span class="highlight">FPGA-based DMA</span> solutions, we provide the tools to break the unbreakable.
				</span>
			</p>
		</section>

		<hr class="divider"/>

		<!-- Section 2: Technical SKILLS (Visual) -->
		<section class="arsenal">
			<h2><span class="glitch-header" data-text="TECHNICAL SKILLS">TECHNICAL SKILLS</span></h2>
			
			<div class="skill-grid">
				<!-- Skill 1 -->
				<div class="skill-item">
					<div class="skill-info">
						<span>Driver Development</span>
						<span class="percentage">60%</span>
					</div>
					<div class="progress-bar">
						<div class="fill" style="--target-width: 60%; animation-delay: 0.2s;"></div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Skill 2 -->
				<div class="skill-item">
					<div class="skill-info">
						<span>Reverse Engineering (IDA)</span>
						<span class="percentage">80%</span>
					</div>
					<div class="progress-bar">
						<div class="fill" style="--target-width: 80%; animation-delay: 0.4s;"></div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Skill 3 -->
				<div class="skill-item">
					<div class="skill-info">
						<span>DMA / FPGA Logic</span>
						<span class="percentage">99%</span>
					</div>
					<div class="progress-bar">
						<div class="fill" style="--target-width: 99%; animation-delay: 0.6s;"></div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Skill 4 -->
				<div class="skill-item">
					<div class="skill-info">
						<span>Anti-Cheat Evasion (EAC/BE/VGK)</span>
						<span class="percentage">99%</span>
					</div>
					<div class="progress-bar">
						<div class="fill" style="--target-width: 99%; animation-delay: 0.8s;"></div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<hr class="divider"/>

		<!-- Section 3: Operations Log (Timeline) -->
		<section class="operations">
			<h2><span class="glitch-header" data-text="OPERATIONS LOG">OPERATIONS LOG</span></h2>
			
			<div class="timeline">
				<div class="entry">
					<div class="date">2025.Q4</div>
					<div class="content">
						<h3>SMM LC AGENT</h3>
						<p>Achieve low-level memory reading and communicate with a remote host through SMM.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="entry">
					<div class="date">2025.Q4</div>
					<div class="content">
						<h3>IOMMU HOOK FIRMWARE</h3>
						<p>Hijacking the IOMMU at the firmware level to bypass anti-cheat checks.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="entry">
					<div class="date">2025.Q4</div>
					<div class="content">
						<h3>AHCI FIRMWARE</h3>
						<p>The pure firmware simulation implements the AHCI controller and hard disk simulation, achieving 100% disk emulation.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="entry">
					<div class="date">2025.Q3</div>
					<div class="content">
						<h3>PCILEECH MCP SERVER</h3>
						<p>The AI MCP server, further advancing the PCILEECH project community.The project has been open-sourced. <!-- <span class="status">UNDETECTED</span>--></p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="entry">
					<div class="date">2025.Q3</div>
					<div class="content">
						<h3>DMA UNBLOCKER</h3>
						<p>By reverse engineering the anti-cheat driver, the anti-cheat protection was bypassed.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="entry">
					<div class="date">2025.Q3</div>
					<div class="content">
						<h3>DMA VTD/IOMMU DETECTED BYPASS</h3>
						<p>By hijacking ACPI, the checks on VTD/IOMMU were bypassed.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="entry">
					<div class="date">2025.Q1</div>
					<div class="content">
						<h3>FIRMWARE CUSTOM REG R/W SYSTEM</h3>
						<p>Made modifications to the PCILEECH-FPGA project to support reading and writing custom registers. The project has been open-sourced.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="entry">
					<div class="date">2025.Q1</div>
					<div class="content">
						<h3>PCILEECH FIRMWARE DMA ENGINE</h3>
						<p>Implemented a custom DMA engine read/write framework under the PCILEECH-FPGA framework.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

	</div>
</Layout>

<style>
	/* Smooth Animated Title */
	.animated-title {
		font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
		font-size: 3rem; /* Make it big */
		font-weight: 800;
		letter-spacing: 2px;
		
		/* Gradient Setup */
		background: linear-gradient(
			90deg, 
			#ffffff 0%, 
			#ffffff 40%, 
			#b026ff 50%, 
			#ffffff 60%, 
			#ffffff 100%
		);
		background-size: 200% auto;
		
		/* Clip background to text */
		color: transparent;
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		background-clip: text;
		
		/* Animation */
		animation: shineFlow 5s linear infinite;
		
		/* Subtle Static Glow */
		text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(176, 38, 255, 0.2);
	}

	@keyframes shineFlow {
		0% { background-position: 200% center; }
		100% { background-position: 0% center; }
	}

	/* Global Profile Styles */
	.profile-container {
		font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
		color: #e0e0e0;
	}

	.highlight {
		color: #b026ff;
		text-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(176, 38, 255, 0.5);
	}

	.divider {
		border: 0;
		height: 1px;
		background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #2a2a35, transparent);
		margin: 3rem 0;
	}

	h2 {
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		font-size: 1.8rem;
		color: #fff;
		border-left: 4px solid #b026ff;
		padding-left: 1rem;
	}

	/* Terminal Text */
	.terminal-text {
		background: rgba(10, 10, 18, 0.8);
		border: 1px solid #333;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 8px;
		line-height: 1.6;
		box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
	}
	.prompt { color: #27c93f; margin-right: 0.5rem; }
	.output { display: block; margin-top: 0.5rem; color: #a0a0b0; }

	/* Skill Grid */
	.skill-grid {
		display: grid;
		gap: 1.5rem;
	}
	.skill-item {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
		padding: 1rem;
		border-radius: 6px;
		border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
		transition: transform 0.2s;
	}
	.skill-item:hover {
		transform: translateX(5px);
		border-color: #b026ff;
	}
	.skill-info {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: space-between;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
		font-weight: bold;
	}
	.percentage { color: #b026ff; }
	
	.progress-bar {
		height: 8px;
		background: #1a1a24;
		border-radius: 4px;
		overflow: hidden;
		position: relative;
	}
	.fill {
		height: 100%;
		background: linear-gradient(90deg, #6a0dad, #b026ff);
		width: 0; /* Animated to full width */
		border-radius: 4px;
		animation: fillBar 1.5s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1) forwards;
		box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(176, 38, 255, 0.5);
	}

	@keyframes fillBar {
		to { width: var(--target-width); } /* JS or Inline style handles the width, keyframe acts as trigger */
	}

	/* Timeline */
	.timeline {
		position: relative;
		padding-left: 2rem;
		border-left: 2px solid #2a2a35;
	}
	.entry {
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		position: relative;
	}
	.entry::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		left: -2.6rem; /* Adjust based on padding/border */
		top: 5px;
		width: 12px;
		height: 12px;
		background: #0a0a12;
		border: 2px solid #b026ff;
		border-radius: 50%;
		box-shadow: 0 0 5px #b026ff;
		transition: background 0.3s;
	}
	.entry:hover::before {
		background: #b026ff;
	}
	.date {
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		color: #b026ff;
		margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
	}
	.content h3 {
		margin: 0;
		font-size: 1.2rem;
		color: #e0e0e0;
	}
	.content p {
		margin: 0.5rem 0 0;
		color: #888;
	}
	.status {
		display: inline-block;
		font-size: 0.7rem;
		padding: 2px 6px;
		background: rgba(39, 201, 63, 0.1);
		color: #27c93f;
		border: 1px solid #27c93f;
		border-radius: 4px;
		margin-left: 0.5rem;
	}

	/* Glitch Header Animation */
	.glitch-header {
		position: relative;
	}
	.glitch-header:hover::before {
		content: attr(data-text);
		position: absolute;
		left: -2px;
		text-shadow: 1px 0 #ff00c1;
		top: 0;
		color: white;
		background: #050508;
		overflow: hidden;
		clip: rect(0, 900px, 0, 0); 
		animation: glitch-anim-2 2s infinite linear alternate-reverse;
	}

</style>
